#. PeterHan.AirlockDoor.AirlockDoorStrings.BUILDING.STATUSITEMS.AIRLOCKSTOREDCHARGE.NAME
msgctxt "PeterHan.AirlockDoor.AirlockDoorStrings.BUILDING.STATUSITEMS.AIRLOCKSTOREDCHARGE.NAME"
msgid "Charge Available: {0}/{1}"
msgstr "사용 가능 전력：{0}/{1}"

#. PeterHan.AirlockDoor.AirlockDoorStrings.BUILDING.STATUSITEMS.AIRLOCKSTOREDCHARGE.TOOLTIP
msgctxt "PeterHan.AirlockDoor.AirlockDoorStrings.BUILDING.STATUSITEMS.AIRLOCKSTOREDCHARGE.TOOLTIP"
msgid "This Airlock has <b>{0}</b> of stored <style=\"KKeyword\">Power</style>\n\nIt consumes up to <style=\"consumed\">{2}</style> per use"
msgstr "저장된 <b>{0}</b>의 <style=\"KKeyword\">전력</style>을 사용할 수 있습니다.\n\n한번 사용할 때 마다 <style=\"consumed\">{2}</style> 만큼의 전력이 소모됩니다."

#. PeterHan.AirlockDoor.AirlockDoorStrings.BUILDINGS.PREFABS.PAIRLOCKDOOR.NAME
msgctxt "PeterHan.AirlockDoor.AirlockDoorStrings.BUILDINGS.PREFABS.PAIRLOCKDOOR.NAME"
msgid "<link=\"PAIRLOCKDOOR\">Airlock Door</link>"
msgstr "<link=\"PAIRLOCKDOOR\">밀폐 에어록</link>"

#. PeterHan.AirlockDoor.AirlockDoorStrings.BUILDINGS.PREFABS.PAIRLOCKDOOR.DESC
msgctxt "PeterHan.AirlockDoor.AirlockDoorStrings.BUILDINGS.PREFABS.PAIRLOCKDOOR.DESC"
msgid "Sucking Duplicants that have nowhere to go into space through <link=\"PRESSUREDOOR\">Mechanized Airlocks</link> is poor taste. Airlock Doors now allow Duplicants safe passage without the loss of any of their mysterious fluids."
msgstr "복제체가 <link=\"PRESSUREDOOR\">기계식 에어록</link>을 사용할 때 마다 유체가 통과하는 것을 방지하여 시설과 복제체 모두 안전한 상태로 통행할 수 있는 특수 에어록입니다.\n이 문을 통해 열이 전도되는 것을 막지는 않습니다."

#. PeterHan.AirlockDoor.AirlockDoorStrings.BUILDINGS.PREFABS.PAIRLOCKDOOR.EFFECT
msgctxt "PeterHan.AirlockDoor.AirlockDoorStrings.BUILDINGS.PREFABS.PAIRLOCKDOOR.EFFECT"
msgid "Blocks <link=\"ELEMENTSLIQUID\">Liquid</link> and <link=\"ELEMENTSGAS\">Gas</link> flow, even while Duplicants are passing.\n\nWill not allow passage when no <link=\"POWER\">Power</link> is available.\n\n<link=\"CRITTERS\">Critters</link> can never pass through this door."
msgstr "복제체가 지나가는 동안 <link=\"ELEMENTSLIQUID\">액체</link>와 <link=\"ELEMENTSGAS\">기체</link>의 흐름을 차단합니다.\n\n충전된 <link=\"POWER\">전력</link>이 부족하면 통과할 수 없습니다.\n\n<link=\"CRITTERS\">동물</link>들은 이 문을 통과할 수 없습니다."

#. PeterHan.AirlockDoor.AirlockDoorStrings.BUILDINGS.PREFABS.PAIRLOCKDOOR.LOGIC_OPEN
msgctxt "PeterHan.AirlockDoor.AirlockDoorStrings.BUILDINGS.PREFABS.PAIRLOCKDOOR.LOGIC_OPEN"
msgid "Unlock/Lock"
msgstr "잠금 해제/잠금"

#. PeterHan.AirlockDoor.AirlockDoorStrings.BUILDINGS.PREFABS.PAIRLOCKDOOR.LOGIC_OPEN_ACTIVE
msgctxt "PeterHan.AirlockDoor.AirlockDoorStrings.BUILDINGS.PREFABS.PAIRLOCKDOOR.LOGIC_OPEN_ACTIVE"
msgid "<b><style=\"logic_on\">Green Signal</style></b>: Unlock door"
msgstr "<b><style=\"logic_on\">녹색 신호</style></b>이 문의 잠금을 해제합니다."

#. PeterHan.AirlockDoor.AirlockDoorStrings.BUILDINGS.PREFABS.PAIRLOCKDOOR.LOGIC_OPEN_INACTIVE
msgctxt "PeterHan.AirlockDoor.AirlockDoorStrings.BUILDINGS.PREFABS.PAIRLOCKDOOR.LOGIC_OPEN_INACTIVE"
msgid "<b><style=\"logic_off\">Red Signal</style></b>: Lock door"
msgstr "<b><style=\"logic_off\">적색 신호</style></b>이 문을 잠급니다."

#. PeterHan.AirlockDoor.AirlockDoorStrings.BUILDINGS.PREFABS.PAIRLOCKDOORINSULATED.NAME
msgctxt "PeterHan.AirlockDoor.AirlockDoorStrings.BUILDINGS.PREFABS.PAIRLOCKDOORINSULATED.NAME"
msgid "<link=\"PAIRLOCKDOORINSULATED\">Insulated Airlock Door</link>"
msgstr "<link=\"PAIRLOCKDOORINSULATED\">단열 밀폐 에어록</link>"

#. PeterHan.AirlockDoor.AirlockDoorStrings.BUILDINGS.PREFABS.PAIRLOCKDOORINSULATED.DESC
msgctxt "PeterHan.AirlockDoor.AirlockDoorStrings.BUILDINGS.PREFABS.PAIRLOCKDOORINSULATED.DESC"
msgid "Sucking Duplicants that have nowhere to go into space through <link=\"PRESSUREDOOR\">Mechanized Airlocks</link> is poor taste. Airlock Doors now allow Duplicants safe passage without the loss of any of their mysterious fluids."
msgstr "복제체가 <link=\"PRESSUREDOOR\">단열 문</link>을 사용할 때 마다 유체가 통과하는 것을 방지하여 시설과 복제체 모두 안전한 상태로 통행할 수 있는 특수 에어록입니다."

#. PeterHan.AirlockDoor.AirlockDoorStrings.BUILDINGS.PREFABS.PAIRLOCKDOORINSULATED.EFFECT
msgctxt "PeterHan.AirlockDoor.AirlockDoorStrings.BUILDINGS.PREFABS.PAIRLOCKDOORINSULATED.EFFECT"
msgid "Blocks <link=\"ELEMENTSLIQUID\">Liquid</link> and <link=\"ELEMENTSGAS\">Gas</link> flow, even while Duplicants are passing.\n\nWill not allow passage when no <link=\"POWER\">Power</link> is available.\n\n<link=\"CRITTERS\">Critters</link> can never pass through this door."
msgstr "복제체가 지나가는 동안 <link=\"ELEMENTSLIQUID\">액체</link>와 <link=\"ELEMENTSGAS\">기체</link>의 흐름을 차단합니다.\n\n충전된 <link=\"POWER\">전력</link>이 부족하면 통과할 수 없습니다.\n\n<link=\"CRITTERS\">동물</link>들은 이 문을 통과할 수 없습니다.\n\n공간 간의 <link=\"HEAT\">열</link>교환을 감소시켜 온도를 조절할 수 있게 합니다."
